{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 403180, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 83319, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "#74578", "timestamp": 1601475320, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 403185, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 83319, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "如果资源够的话，没几个人会无穷尽地卷下去。绝大部分人都会在某个地方停下脚步", "timestamp": 1601475460, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 403201, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 83319, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 每个人觉得自己过得好坏很大程度上是和别人比的。从某些物质指标衡量，现在的普通人比古代皇帝过的好多了。只要资源有限（不是无穷）就必然卷，资源是不可能“够”的。", "timestamp": 1601475856, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 403216, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 83319, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 就稍微离谱一点（也没离谱太多\n假如给每个进清华的同学毕业了给百万年薪\n有多少人会放弃卷，而去躺平\n所以每个人都有一个够的标准，目前平均资源还远远没达到够", "timestamp": 1601476053, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 403222, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 83319, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 这倒也是，看你在什么集合里面比了", "timestamp": 1601476108, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 403229, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 83319, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 相对剥夺了解一下，只有平均主义才能解", "timestamp": 1601476215, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 403245, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 83319, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 平均主义多半导致资源总量下降", "timestamp": 1601476595, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 403246, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 83319, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 可以把各位相互剥夺的内部矛盾转化为统一对外的矛盾\n（指若清华蛋糕远大于清华外蛋糕\n其实应当扩大到整个社会范围内，不过这样没必要讨论卷了，弱肉强食就是自然规则", "timestamp": 1601476594, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 2, "pid": 83319, "reply": 8, "tag": null, "text": "内卷的原因，不是资源太少，而是每个人都想过得更好。这里的好可以粗略认为是个人占有总资源的比例。", "timestamp": 1601475094, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1606782627, "url": "", "vote": {}}}